---
title: Cal Smart Fig-Glazed Double Pork Meatballs with Brussels Sprouts and Garlic Sauce
description: Time to get figgy with it! In this calorie-conscious meal, fig-glazed pork meatballs adorn couscous studded with cranberries and nutrient-dense Brussels sprouts. A drizzle of zesty garlic sauce brings home the flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cal-smart-fig-glazed-double-pork-meatballs-ccc210ed.jpg
